Helo?

578
00:45:30,400 --> 00:45:31,280
Tuan?

579
00:45:37,040 --> 00:45:38,680
Okey. Tolak!

580
00:45:50,080 --> 00:45:50,960
Maaf.

581
00:45:52,720 --> 00:45:53,640
Siapa kau?

582
00:45:53,720 --> 00:45:57,600
Saya dihantar dari tingkat atas.
Saya pembantu baharu tuan.

583
00:46:03,320 --> 00:46:04,480
Akram Salim.

584
00:46:08,960 --> 00:46:10,000
DC Dixon.

585
00:46:10,080 --> 00:46:12,000
Kenapa aku rasa kau sebabnya?

586
00:46:12,080 --> 00:46:13,680
Jadi, kau dah jumpa Akram.

587
00:46:13,760 --> 00:46:16,000
Kau nak buat lawak?

588
00:46:16,080 --> 00:46:18,400
Dia sangat bersemangat.

589
00:46:18,480 --> 00:46:21,240
Ya, itu kata lain untuk menyusahkan.

590
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:24,080
Kau berdua mesti serasi.

591
00:46:25,240 --> 00:46:26,560
Biar betul…

592
00:46:30,120 --> 00:46:32,360
- Akram, ya?
- Ya, tuan.

593
00:46:32,440 --> 00:46:37,120
Carl. Bukan "tuan". Aku sangat sibuk.
Banyak yang perlu dibuat.

594
00:46:37,200 --> 00:46:39,360
Sebab itu saya di sini, tuan. Carl.

595
00:46:40,040 --> 00:46:43,520
Bagus. Okey. Ada mop dan baldi di sana.
Tempat ini bersepah.

596
00:46:43,600 --> 00:46:46,360
Kemudian, naik atas dan ambil untuk aku…

597
00:46:49,560 --> 00:46:53,680
komputer dan televisyen baharu.

598
00:46:57,200 --> 00:46:59,520
- Itu saja?
- Buat masa sekarang.

599
00:47:09,040 --> 00:47:10,040
DCI Morck.

600
00:47:24,360 --> 00:47:26,760
Hei. Aku datang.

601
00:47:30,240 --> 00:47:34,160
Mereka kata kau jatuh dari katil.
Jumpa kau di lantai tepi tingkap.

602
00:47:38,000 --> 00:47:39,800
Tak tahu udara Scotland berbahaya?

603
00:47:49,560 --> 00:47:50,400
Pergi jahanam.

604
00:47:50,480 --> 00:47:51,480
Tolonglah.

605
00:47:52,560 --> 00:47:54,400
Tolonglah aku.

606
00:47:55,560 --> 00:47:58,920
Kita akan cari jalan,
macam biasa. Aku janji.

607
00:47:59,000 --> 00:48:00,640
Itu Carl Morck?

608
00:48:01,400 --> 00:48:02,520
Hei.

609
00:48:02,600 --> 00:48:04,640
- Ayah.
- Hei!

610
00:49:05,120 --> 00:49:05,960
Helo.

611
00:49:08,720 --> 00:49:09,720
Helo?

612
00:49:14,480 --> 00:49:15,480
Claire?

613
00:49:19,000 --> 00:49:21,200
Claire? Apa…

614
00:49:21,720 --> 00:49:24,360
Saya cuba hubungi awak. Awak lambat.

615
00:49:25,840 --> 00:49:26,800
William.

616
00:49:28,920 --> 00:49:29,800
William.

617
00:49:32,400 --> 00:49:33,400
Boleh tengok?

618
00:49:42,160 --> 00:49:46,000
Tak apa. Lembut.

619
00:49:56,120 --> 00:49:57,560
Apa itu? Bot ayah?

620
00:50:14,320 --> 00:50:18,080
Kakak tak tahu apa kamu rasa,
tapi kakak penat.

621
00:50:21,760 --> 00:50:24,120
Mungkin kita patut pergi seketika.

622
00:50:25,920 --> 00:50:27,800
Beralih angin. Mahu tak?

623
